ygData.subject: Re: Digest Number 129
ygData.msgSnippet: Alright, as I said, I would not change it for ONE person, however many people, I will... I still don t see how a few extra lines are that all imposing,
ygData.messageBody:
Alright, as I said, I would not change it for ONE person, however many
people, I will... I still don't see how a few extra lines are that all
imposing, especially when you can scroll by them in one hundredth of a
second, but if your all that annoyed then fine.. ive removed all of the
oxymorons that I find so funny, so all you lazy ppl that cant scroll, your
wish is my command, as for the random characters people speak of, I have no
clue how to get rid of them, and YES I do use outlook Express and ive been
told it has something to do with that. As for me being on peoples kill
lists, thats fine with me.. no skin off my back, I'm just here to pick up
any extra knowledge, however I myself have a great deal of knowledge.. and
im not just blowing my horn either. +ACo-shrug

Wes Lobdell,
Note: I'm not a Mac person, but you have to admit, the following is funny+ACEAIQ-
:) And if you don't +ACI-get+ACI- it, then I guess the media hasn't soaked it for
all its worth yet after all...
Quote: +ACI-Macintosh -- we might not get everything right, but
atleast we knew the century was going to end.+ACI-
